snippet.title: Identifying Ghosts with NO EVIDENCE - Phasmophobia No Evidence Marathon
snippet.description:
Welcome back to Phasmophobia! In this video we do a MEGA No Evidence marathon. No Evidence is the best challenge in the game in my opinion! In this challenge you have to figure out the ghost based purely on behaviour (without using any evidence item). This teaches you a lot about the game. I've played this game for over 1500 hours and this is the ultimate test of skill! I really hope you enjoy. Much love and see you during the streams :D
